data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!!! Motivated Sellers!!! Bring ALL reasonable offers!!! Welcome to 245 Bayberry Dr! This gorgeous 4 bedroom 3 1/2 bath home is situated on an OVERSIZED half acre lot located in the HIGHLY sought after neighborhood of Sandy Pointe! Bring your boat, jet ski, or pontoon & enjoy all of the amenities of living in a lakefront community! Beautifully well kept homes, low yearly HOA, friendly neighbors, a community boat ramp & dock to enjoy the beautiful 376 acre Lake Agnes. The location is IDEAL for commuting to either Orlando, or Tampa with direct access to i4 and other neighboring cities including Lakeland, Auburndale, & Kissimmee all within a 25 minute drive. You will notice the great attention to detail and love put into this home as soon as you enter. The open and inviting kitchen is great for hosting family and friends for holidays, and large gatherings, with great features including solid wood cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. This triple split floor plan will offer you both privacy & functionality with one of the bedrooms also having it's own en-suite bathroom making it ideal for multi-generational living or perfect for the teenager in your household. Spend your evenings relaxing on the screened in back patio overlooking your private backyard oasis or enjoy the FL sunshine with no worries of being sunburnt, as the patio was recently installed with 80% UV blocking screen panels! This home has truly been so well kept and taken care of and is ready for it's new owners! **Assumable Loan low interest rate option** Contact agent for more details!
